# Android release signing.
# This is a PRIVATE repo and the DEV/TEST keystore is committed deliberately so a
# fresh clone can rebuild release APKs with the SAME signature (Android requires
# the same key to update an already-installed app). If this repo is ever made
# public or the app ships to a store, ROTATE this key and purge it from history.
# General keystores stay ignored; only the one dev key + its props are tracked.
*.jks
*.keystore
!android/app/linkhub-release.jks
!android/keystore.properties
*.log
.DS_Store
# iOS build artifacts (generated by ios/scripts/build-core-ios.sh + Xcode/XcodeGen)
ios/Frameworks/
ios/LinkHub.xcodeproj/
ios/DerivedData/
*.xcframework
Thumbs.db
# Screenshots / scratch captures — kept in a dedicated local folder, never committed
.screenshots/
phone-*.png
# AI handoff notes / worklog — committed to this PRIVATE repo so a future AI that
# clones it inherits the full per-session history, decisions, and known risks.

